The Oversight Committee shall be composed of the following members:
2 members of the North County Land Trust;
1 delegate to the Greater Pasadena Council who represents a waterfront community;
1 member of the Pasadena Sport Fishermen's Group;
1 member of the Anne Arundel County Watermen's Association;
1 member of the Maryland Saltwater Sport Fishermen's Association;
1 individual who represents the pleasure boating industry in Anne Arundel County;
1 member of the Pasadena Business Association;
1 resident of legislative district 31; and
1 resident of legislative district 47A.
